==English==

===Noun===
'''Kabyle'''

# A [[w:Northern Berber languages|Northern Berber language]] of the [[Berber]] branch of the [[w:Afro-Asiatic languages|Afro-Asiatic language]] family, spoken by over 3,000,000 people in [[Algeria]]; native name native name ''taqbaylit'' (θāqbāylīθ) ({{ARchar|[[ثاقبايليث]]}}).
# A member of the ethnic group that speaks this language.

